TITLE: Implementing Exit Animations with HTML Classes
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create exit animations using animate-out combined with fade-out, spin-out, zoom-out, and slide-out utilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jamiebuilds/tailwindcss-animate/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<button class="animate-out fade-out ...">Button A</button>
<button class="animate-out spin-out ...">Button B</button>
<button class="animate-out zoom-out ...">Button C</button>
<button class="animate-out slide-out-from-top ...">Button D</button>
<button class="animate-out slide-out-from-left ...">Button E</button>
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Controlling Animation Iteration Count with HTML Classes
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use repeat-{amount} utilities to control an element's animation-iteration-count property.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jamiebuilds/tailwindcss-animate/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<button class="animate-bounce repeat-0 ...">Button A</button>
<button class="animate-bounce repeat-1 ...">Button B</button>
<button class="animate-bounce repeat-infinite ...">Button C</button>
```

