TITLE: Configuring tailwindcss-animate in Tailwind Config
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add the tailwindcss-animate plugin to the Tailwind CSS configuration file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jamiebuilds/tailwindcss-animate/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
// @filename tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
	theme: {
		// ...
	},
	plugins: [
		require("tailwindcss-animate"),
		// ...
	],
}
```

