TITLE: Customizing Animation Timing Functions in Tailwind Config
DESCRIPTION: Configuration example showing how to extend the default animation timing function utilities in a Tailwind CSS project. Adds custom exponential easing functions to the theme configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jamiebuilds/tailwindcss-animate/blob/main/docs/zh/docs/animation-timing-function.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
// @filename tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
    theme: {
        extend: {
            animationTimingFunction: {
                "in-expo": "cubic-bezier(0.95, 0.05, 0.795, 0.035)",
                "out-expo": "cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1)",
            },
        },
    },
}
```

