TITLE: Customizing Animation Timing Functions in Tailwind Config
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript configuration for extending the default animation timing function theme with custom cubic-bezier values for exponential easing in and out effects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jamiebuilds/tailwindcss-animate/blob/main/docs/animation-timing-function.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// @filename tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
	theme: {
		extend: {
			animationTimingFunction: {
				"in-expo": "cubic-bezier(0.95, 0.05, 0.795, 0.035)",
				"out-expo": "cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1)",
			},
		},
	},
}
```

